  "detailed_description": "Play with 4-8 players online, get points for every track you win, and be the next champion!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe recommend playing with friends online using voice chat.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo win the championship, receive points in every track based on race position.<br />\r\nThere are 9 different tracks, with loops and spikes that you need to avoid.<br />\r\nDrop bombs typing \"B\" so you can blow enemies!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nReach the end of the track and wait for the others while playing a \"capture the flag\" game and collect extra points!!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures<br />\r\nCustomization: Pick your racer",
  "about_the_game": "Play with 4-8 players online, get points for every track you win, and be the next champion!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe recommend playing with friends online using voice chat.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo win the championship, receive points in every track based on race position.<br />\r\nThere are 9 different tracks, with loops and spikes that you need to avoid.<br />\r\nDrop bombs typing \"B\" so you can blow enemies!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nReach the end of the track and wait for the others while playing a \"capture the flag\" game and collect extra points!!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures<br />\r\nCustomization: Pick your racer",
